{"tid":1157172,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手買望遠鏡","createTime":"2019-05-16T05:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T04:10:30.000Z","uid":233015,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a529690327145072b5deeda9ebc5241b6076e9c","tid":1157172,"uid":233015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"新手想試下觀天，暫時諗住睇下月球， 好彩就睇埋土星果啲。<br />\n<br />\n考慮緊買雙筒定天文望遠鏡。今次主要想問天文望遠鏡。 <br />\n<br />\n暫時睇緊3吋~4吋，因為折射式太長，唔方便帶上巴士，暫時考慮反射式。<br />\n<br />\n但我見平價細口徑反射式($2000樓下) 好似主鏡好多都冇collimation screws,  咁collimation只做副鏡都足夠？<br />\n<br />\n另下想問DOB裝三腳架可唔可行？ 可行的話方唔方便？<br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab25707ee67b793f7053669fcaaf64ed1935effb","tid":1157172,"uid":233015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a529690327145072b5deeda9ebc5241b6076e9c","tid":1157172,"uid":233015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"新手想試下觀天，暫時諗住睇下月球， 好彩就睇埋土星果啲。<br />\n<br />\n考慮緊買雙筒定天文望遠鏡。今次主要想問天文望遠鏡。 <br />\n<br />\n暫時睇緊3吋~4吋，因為折射式太長，唔方便帶上巴士，暫時考慮反射式。<br />\n<br />\n但我見平價細口徑反射式($2000樓下) 好似主鏡好多都冇collimation screws,  咁collimation只做副鏡都足夠？<br />\n<br />\n另下想問DOB裝三腳架可唔可行？ 可行的話方唔方便？<br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"補充多句， 我想dob裝三腳架係因為我見就咁用三腳架果啲鏡又要counter weight,  又要經緯儀， 好似好煩咁。 觀月我諗人手aim都足夠。"},{"pid":"ba454edd1bd2fa49479c08f32fc2b3a9ce14ff03","tid":1157172,"uid":198958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"我得枝折射<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果要細小，不如牛頓，不過每次都要對光軸"},{"pid":"0f1181c744fc2f2744b5609c2a6415602a1c4c05","tid":1157172,"uid":1989